name: US Oxygen Supply
overview:
We Offer Industrial, Speciality, & Medical Gases and Gas Delivery to Businesses in the Dallas/ Ft Worth Area.

We provide hospitals, surgery clinics as well as animal hospitals and veterinarian with medical gases and is vastly becoming a leading choice for customers who demand a higher quality of service and want a vendor that honestly cares about their business and does so with quality care. Our executive team has more than 50 years of experience in the medical and medical gas field, and offer training to a variety of healthcare practitioners.

We also offer industrial gas to welding companies who benefit from our extensive product catalog of welding gases, welding supplies, metals, safety supplies, personal protective equipment and tools.
